query: SELECT ct.conname, ct.conkey, ct.confkey, nl.nspname AS fknsp, cl.relname AS fktab, nr.nspname AS refnsp, cr.relname AS reftab FROM pg_constraint ct JOIN pg_class cl ON cl.oid = ct.conrelid JOIN pg_namespace nl ON nl.oid = cl.relnamespace JOIN pg_class cr ON cr.oid = ct.confrelid JOIN pg_namespace nr ON nr.oid = cr.relnamespace JOIN pg_catalog.pg_namespace nc ON nc.oid = ct.connamespace WHERE contype=$2 AND nc.nspname = $1
COPY (SELECT * FROM pg_stat_all_indexes) TO stdout WITH CSV HEADER
SELECT spcname AS tablespace_name, pg_catalog.pg_tablespace_size(oid) / $1 AS tablespace_size_mb FROM pg_catalog.pg_tablespace
SELECT COALESCE(sum($1), $2) AS number_of_prepared_transactions FROM pg_catalog.pg_prepared_xacts
COPY (SELECT * FROM pg_stat_database) TO stdout WITH CSV HEADER
SELECT c.relname AS sequence_name FROM pg_catalog.pg_class c, pg_catalog.pg_namespace n WHERE c.relkind = $2 AND c.relnamespace = n.oid AND n.nspname = $1
COPY (SELECT * FROM pg_stat_all_tables) TO stdout WITH CSV HEADER
COPY (SELECT * FROM pg_stat_all_indexes) TO stdout WITH CSV HEADER
COPY (SELECT * FROM pg_stat_all_tables) TO stdout WITH CSV HEADER
COPY (SELECT * FROM pg_stat_database) TO stdout WITH CSV HEADER
